<sect>
<heading>What this chapter covers</heading>
<p>
This chapter tells you about programming with Debian GNU/Linux. The first
part of this chapter gives a short introduction into the currently widely
used languages perl, c, and c++. The second part gives an overview on the
other possibilies to program with Debian GNU/Linux.
</sect>

